Help on function SignatureHash in module bitcoin.core.script:

SSiiggnnaattuurreeHHaasshh(script, txTo, inIdx, hashtype, amount=None, sigversion=0)
    Calculate a signature hash
    
    'Cooked' version that checks if inIdx is out of bounds - this is *not*
    consensus-correct behavior, but is what you probably want for general
    wallet use.
